{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Last year here at TED"},{"time":2000,"text":"I asked you to give me your data,"},{"time":4000,"text":"to put your data on the web, on the basis"},{"time":6000,"text":"that if people put data onto the web --"},{"time":9000,"text":"government data, scientific data, community data,"},{"time":12000,"text":"whatever it is -- it will be used by other people"},{"time":14000,"text":"to do wonderful things, in ways"},{"time":16000,"text":"that they never could have imagined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"So, today I'm back just to show you a few things,"},{"time":21000,"text":"to show you, in fact, there is"},{"time":23000,"text":"an open data movement afoot,"},{"time":28000,"text":"now, around the world."},{"time":30000,"text":"The cry of \"Raw data now!\""},{"time":32000,"text":"which I made people make in the auditorium,"},{"time":34000,"text":"was heard around the world."},{"time":36000,"text":"So, let's roll the video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"A classic story, the first one which lots of people picked up,"},{"time":42000,"text":"was when in March -- on March 10th in fact, soon after TED --"},{"time":45000,"text":"Paul Clarke, in the U.K. government,"},{"time":48000,"text":"blogged, \"Oh, I've just got some raw data. Here it is,"},{"time":50000,"text":"it's about bicycle accidents.\""},{"time":53000,"text":"Two days it took the Times Online"},{"time":56000,"text":"to make a map, a mashable map --"},{"time":58000,"text":"we call these things mash-ups --"},{"time":60000,"text":"a mashed-up user interface that allows you to go in there"},{"time":62000,"text":"and have a look and find out whether your bicycle"},{"time":64000,"text":"route to work was affected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"Here's more data, traffic survey data,"},{"time":68000,"text":"again, put out by the U.K. government,"},{"time":70000,"text":"and because they put it up using the Linked Data standards,"},{"time":73000,"text":"then a user could just make a map,"},{"time":75000,"text":"just by clicking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"Does this data affect things? Well, let's get back to 2008."},{"time":79000,"text":"Look at Zanesville, Ohio."},{"time":82000,"text":"Here's a map a lawyer made. He put on it the water plant,"},{"time":85000,"text":"and which houses are there,"},{"time":87000,"text":"which houses have been connected to the water."},{"time":89000,"text":"And he got, from other data sources,"},{"time":91000,"text":"information to show"},{"time":94000,"text":"which houses are occupied by white people."},{"time":96000,"text":"Well, there was too much of a correlation, he felt,"},{"time":99000,"text":"between which houses were occupied by white people"},{"time":102000,"text":"and which houses had water, and the judge was not impressed either."},{"time":105000,"text":"The judge was not impressed to the tune of 10.9 million dollars."},{"time":108000,"text":"That's the power of taking one piece of data,"},{"time":110000,"text":"another piece of data, putting it together,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and showing the result."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"Let's look at some data from the U.K. now."},{"time":117000,"text":"This is U.K. government data, a completely independent site,"},{"time":119000,"text":"Where Does My Money Go."},{"time":121000,"text":"It allows anybody to go there and burrow down."},{"time":123000,"text":"You can burrow down by a particular type of spending,"},{"time":125000,"text":"or you can go through all the different regions and compare them."},{"time":129000,"text":"So, that's happening in the U.K. with U.K. government data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"Yes, certainly you can do it over here."},{"time":134000,"text":"Here's a site which allows you to look at recovery spending"},{"time":137000,"text":"in California."},{"time":139000,"text":"Take an arbitrary example, Long Beach, California,"},{"time":141000,"text":"you can go and have a look at what recovery money they've been spending"},{"time":144000,"text":"on different things such as energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"In fact, this is the graph of the number of data sets"},{"time":150000,"text":"in the repositories of data.gov,"},{"time":152000,"text":"and data.gov.uk."},{"time":154000,"text":"And I'm delighted to see a great competition"},{"time":156000,"text":"between the U.K. in blue, and the U.S. in red."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"How can you use this stuff?"},{"time":160000,"text":"Well, for example, if you have lots of data about places"},{"time":163000,"text":"you can take, from a postcode --"},{"time":165000,"text":"which is like a zip plus four --"},{"time":167000,"text":"for a specific group of houses, you can make paper,"},{"time":170000,"text":"print off a paper which has got very, very"},{"time":172000,"text":"specific things about the bus stops,"},{"time":174000,"text":"the things specifically near you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"On a larger scale, this is a mash-up"},{"time":179000,"text":"of the data which was released about the Afghan elections."},{"time":182000,"text":"It allows you to set your own criteria"},{"time":184000,"text":"for what sort of things you want to look at."},{"time":186000,"text":"The red circles are polling stations,"},{"time":188000,"text":"selected by your criteria."},{"time":190000,"text":"And then you can select also other things on the map"},{"time":192000,"text":"to see what other factors, like the threat level."},{"time":194000,"text":"So, that was government data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"I also talked about community-generated data -- in fact I edited some."},{"time":199000,"text":"This is the wiki map, this is the Open Street Map."},{"time":201000,"text":"\"Terrace Theater\" I actually put"},{"time":203000,"text":"on the map because it wasn't on the map before TED last year."},{"time":206000,"text":"I was not the only person editing the open street map."},{"time":209000,"text":"Each flash on this visualization --"},{"time":211000,"text":"put together by ITO World --"},{"time":213000,"text":"shows an edit in 2009"},{"time":215000,"text":"made to the Open Street Map."},{"time":217000,"text":"Let's now spin the world during the same year."},{"time":220000,"text":"Every flash is an edit. Somebody somewhere"},{"time":222000,"text":"looking at the Open Street Map, and realizing it could be better."},{"time":225000,"text":"You can see Europe is ablaze with updates."},{"time":228000,"text":"Some places, perhaps not as much as they should be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"Here focusing in on Haiti."},{"time":233000,"text":"The map of Port au-Prince at the end"},{"time":235000,"text":"of 2009 was not all it could be,"},{"time":237000,"text":"not as good as the map of California."},{"time":239000,"text":"Fortunately, just after the earthquake,"},{"time":242000,"text":"GeoEye, a commercial company,"},{"time":244000,"text":"released satellite imagery"},{"time":246000,"text":"with a license, which allowed"},{"time":248000,"text":"the open-source community to use it."},{"time":250000,"text":"This is January, in time lapse,"},{"time":252000,"text":"of people editing ... that's the earthquake."},{"time":254000,"text":"After the earthquake, immediately,"},{"time":256000,"text":"people all over the world, mappers"},{"time":258000,"text":"who wanted to help, and could,"},{"time":260000,"text":"looked at that imagery, built the map, quickly building it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"We're focusing now on Port-au-Prince."},{"time":264000,"text":"The light blue is refugee camps these volunteers had spotted from the [satellite images]."},{"time":268000,"text":"So, now we have, immediately, a real-time map"},{"time":270000,"text":"showing where there are refugee camps --"},{"time":272000,"text":"rapidly became the best map"},{"time":274000,"text":"to use if you're doing relief work in Port-au-Prince."},{"time":277000,"text":"Witness the fact that it's here on this Garmin device"},{"time":279000,"text":"being used by rescue team in Haiti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281000,"text":"There's the map showing,"},{"time":284000,"text":"on the left-hand side,"},{"time":286000,"text":"that hospital -- actually that's a hospital ship."},{"time":288000,"text":"This is a real-time map that shows blocked roads,"},{"time":291000,"text":"damaged buildings, refugee camps --"},{"time":293000,"text":"it shows things that are needed [for rescue and relief work]."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295000,"text":"So, if you've been involved in that at all,"},{"time":297000,"text":"I just wanted to say: Whatever you've been doing,"},{"time":299000,"text":"whether you've just been chanting, \"Raw data now!\""},{"time":301000,"text":"or you've been putting government or scientific data online,"},{"time":304000,"text":"I just wanted to take this opportunity to say: Thank you very much,"},{"time":306000,"text":"and we have only just started!"},{"time":309000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}